title: A Two Year Old, Another Two Year Old and Satan Ruled Out
itunes:title: A Two Year Old, Another Two Year Old and Satan Ruled Out
description:
Anthony and Gregg discuss what they would do to a two year old if it shredded $1000 and relate to Antonio Brown throwing furniture off a patio. Rest assured, Satan was ruled out when experts were studying a flaming pit in Arkansas.
